text: Derry Olympic Football Club was a football team from Derry, Ireland that was a member of the Irish League for the 1892–93 season. The team was selected from players in the County Londonderry area. ==References== Category:Association football clubs in Derry Urban Area Category:Defunct association football clubs in Northern Ireland Category:Association football clubs established in 1891 Category:Association football clubs disestablished in 1893 Category:Defunct Irish Football League clubs Category:Association football clubs in County Londonderry Category:1891 establishments in Ireland Category:1893 disestablishments in Ireland Category:Former senior Irish Football League clubs
